drh added on 2015-01-09 00:43:34:
Michal Zalewski found several crashing bugs by running a fuzzer against
SQLite and reported them on the mailing list, moments ago.
Each of the following four statements causes a crash:
SELECT n()AND+#00;
SELECT(SELECT strftime());
DETACH(SELECT group_concat(q));
CREATE TABLE t0(t); INSERT INTO t0 SELECT strftime();
